data.description: SPECTACULAR HOME WITH VIEW OF THE BAKER HOTEL.  NEWLY REMODELED WITH GRANITE COUNTER TOPS, TOP GRADE WINDOWS, LAMINATE FLOORING, NEW HOT WATER HEATER, NEW PAINT, AND MUCH MORE.  LOCATED IN HIGHLY SOUGHT AFTER NORTHWEST MOUNTAIN AREA.  THERE'S PLENTY OF ROOM FOR A LARGE FAMILY WITH 4 BEDROOMS, 3 FULL BATHS, SUNROOM, OFFICE AND A HUGE LIVING AND KITCHEN AREA WITH AN OPEN CONCEPT.  IT ALSO HAS A SEPERATE LAUNDRY ROOM AND HAS CUSTOM BUILT BARN DOORS.  HURRY THIS ONE IS A GEM AND WON'T LAST LONG. AGENT IS SELLER
